{"tid":799129,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【迷戀骷髏】切鼻割雙耳 劏舌頭紋眼窩 22歲狂男︰我係正常人","createTime":"2018-08-29T22:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T00:01:43.000Z","uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f043eb8082f22af50381c24a7a810e5d5344d88f","tid":799129,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T22:14:15.000Z","msg":"他有張非一般的臉容，喜歡的人會抓著他合照，不喜歡的人會避之則吉－－哥倫比亞22歲男子深深喜愛骷髏骨，為了讓自己酷似骷髏頭，他花了2年時間紋身整容，甘願削去半個鼻、割去雙耳，加上面上種種紋身，就是想讓自己看來更像一個骷髏頭。<br />\n<br />\n22歲的拉米雷斯（Eric Ram&iacute;rez）是紋身愛好者，全身上下分佈著大大小小的紋身，眉心、下唇等地方穿了環，不過最讓人注目的是其面孔，為了變成他心愛的骷髏骨，他削去半個鼻子，割去雙耳，亦將舌頭割成左右兩半並改為藍灰色，眼睛四周紋上大黑圈以肖似骷髏上的空洞眼窩<br />\n<br />\n拉米雷斯表示自小已愛上骷髏頭，連藝名姓氏也改為骷髏「Kalaca Skull」，他表示是在母親過世後才開始「改頭換臉」。他稱：<span style=\"color: red;\">身體改造是個人決定，不應受世俗審判，那就像批評女人隆胸或隆臀一樣。</span>對我來說骷髏就像我的姊妹，是我家庭的一分子。」對於為何想看似骷髏，他就指因為<span style=\"color: red;\">全人類的皮膚下，又或死後都是一具骷髏。</span> <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180830&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58619465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180830%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58619465&d=Zv7mRUQtUzp1GiUzrZYPeZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=0d2fce17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180830%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58619465&h=4d7d0a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180830&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58619465</a><br />\n<br />\n人哋只不過做自己鍾意、 一直想追求嘅事 ，嗰啲人嘅comment使唔使咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/061102_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F061102_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=19821a65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b308c4d8ab0f914454c1167cc186ef048bdd676","tid":799129,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T22:29:48.000Z","msg":"應該精神／認知有問題"},{"pid":"d69bf9a2e19b1dfe62d3314267b85fdcd5c8a123","tid":799129,"uid":37348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T22:35:32.000Z","msg":"尊重佢去追求佢喜歡嘅事物<br />\n但問題係佢戇鳩到搞咁多野根本唔似骷髏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7da1a17bb05e6a4386d5dff24be04c5cf2f2b5c","tid":799129,"uid":1652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T23:39:14.000Z","msg":"佢近視點算，戴唔到眼鏡焗住戴con"},{"pid":"e3e5d0dc0271ac752021cadf576216ad1adb9ccb","tid":799129,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"好柒"},{"pid":"c435a60c13059d099da3c807ff9931a2402e59d3","tid":799129,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:01:43.000Z","msg":"鬼佬型啲<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/55253367/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F55253367%2Foriginal.jpg&h=ef7bacdf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}